---
import { SectionHeader } from "../../components";
---

<section class="summary-section">
  <SectionHeader
    eyebrow="Professional Summary"
    title="Technical change, connected thinking and delivery-focused problem solving"
  />

  <div class="summary-copy">
    <p>
      I specialise in delivering technical change across IP communications,
      digital transformation and data-driven decision making. My experience spans
      project delivery, product ownership and technical subject matter expertise
      across IP communications, CRM, software development, data analytics and
      cybersecurity.
    </p>

    <p>
      I take pride in never backing down from a new challenge and in building a
      solid technical understanding of every product, platform or project I work
      on. I'm very much a "Never Stop Never Stopping" kind of person; always
      curious, always learning and always looking for the next opportunity to
      improve.
    </p>

    <p>
      Rather than presenting isolated skills or job titles, this portfolio
      explores how those experiences connect through real projects, technologies,
      outcomes and the lessons learned along the way.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .summary-section {
    margin-block: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
  }

  .summary-copy {
    max-width: 920px;
  }

  .summary-copy p {
    max-width: none;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.15rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .summary-copy p + p {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }
</style>